%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20hidden%20consequence%20of%20the%20return-to-office%20crackdown%20%E2%80%94%20more%20workers%20will%20lose%20their%20jobs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22remote%20work%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60897c413f0560001881c863%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERemote%20workers%20face%20being%20fired%20if%20they%20don't%20comply%20with%20return-to-office%20mandates.%3Cp%3EJohner%20Images%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDon't%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20office%3F%20Prepare%20to%20lose%20your%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThat's%20the%20message%20from%20bosses%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20push%20to%20get%20workers%20back%20to%20offices%20could%20put%20millions%20of%20jobs%20at%20risk%20if%20people%20don't%20comply.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20starting%20to%20look%20like%20the%20cruelest%20summer%20for%20millions%20of%20workers%20as%20they%20either%20reluctantly%20wave%20goodbye%20to%20sunny%20freedom%20%E2%80%94%20or%20risk%20incurring%20the%20wrath%20of%20their%20managers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20Wall%20Street%2C%20employers%20are%20preparing%20to%20be%20unforgiving%2C%20mean-spirited%2C%20and%20downright%20vindictive%20with%20any%20workers%20planning%20on%20getting%20in%20the%20way%20of%20their%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-making-workers-employees-return-to-office-rto-wfh-hybrid-2023-1%5C%22%3Ereturn-to-office%20crackdown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%C2%A0looks%20set%20to%20culminate%20just%20after%20Labor%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20began%2C%20millions%20of%20white-collar%20Americans%20have%20come%20to%20expect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fare-remote-jobs-more-productive-work-life-balance-return-office-2023-8%5C%22%3Eremote%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20given%20in%20their%20working%20lives.%20They%20operate%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20employers%20trust%20they'll%20get%20their%20work%20done%20in%20their%20own%20space%20while%20juggling%20childcare%2C%20errands%2C%20and%20the%20odd%20lunchtime%20workout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20more%20workers%20have%20started%20to%20return%20to%20offices%20in%20some%20capacity%2C%20but%20that%20has%20not%20been%20the%20result%20of%20severe%20compulsion%20or%20because%20remote%20work%20has%20fallen%20out%20of%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20monthly%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Stanford%20University%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20MIT%2C%20and%20the%20ITAM%20University%20in%20Mexico%20found%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwfhresearch.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWFHResearch_updates_August2023.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20residents%20enjoyed%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20their%20paid%20full%20days%20at%20home%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20signaling%20the%20persistence%20of%20remote%20work%20more%20than%20three%20years%20after%20the%20pandemic%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20seems%20like%20employers%20have%20had%20enough.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20mandates%20to%20get%20workers%20back%20into%20the%20office%20are%20becoming%20more%20aggressive%20in%20the%20face%20of%20an%20economic%20downturn%20that%20has%20rattled%20CEOs%20grappling%20with%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-jobs-at-risk-replacement-artificial-intelligence-ai-labor-trends-2023-02%5C%22%3Ethe%20threat%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20growing%20tilt%20towards%20protectionism%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20comply%20with%20these%20mandates%20now%20seems%20to%20mean%20one%20thing%3A%20getting%20fired.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20return-to-office%20drive%20is%20about