l%20Street%20bosses%20are%20getting%20more%20serious%20about%20return-to-office%20mandates%20by%20threatening%20to%20fire%20workers%20who%20don't%20comply.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchowdhury%40insider.com%20(Hasan%20Chowdhury)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-crackdown-tech-jobs-at-risk-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Student-loan%20repayment%20is%20about%20to%20be%20'more%20affordable%20than%20ever%20before'%20through%20a%20new%20plan%20that%20will%20cut%20monthly%20payments%20to%20%240%20for%20those%20making%20under%20%2415%20an%20hour%2C%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Biden%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6377f3e891af1b0018f3f804%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden.%3Cp%3ESusan%20Walsh%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBiden%20officially%20launched%20the%20new%20income-driven%20student-loan%20repayment%20plan%2C%20known%20as%20the%20SAVE%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHis%20administration%20said%20the%20plan%20will%20ensure%20anyone%20making%20%2415%20an%20hour%20or%20less%20will%20have%20%240%20payments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20estimates%2020%20million%20borrowers%20will%20benefit%20from%20the%20new%20plan%2C%20which%20would%20save%20them%20%241%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%20the%20student-loan%20payment%20pause%20ends%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20officially%20launched%20his%20new%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Biden's%20administration%20announced%20that%20student-loan%20borrowers%20can%20now%20officially%20enroll%20in%20the%20Saving%20on%20a%20Valuable%20Education%2C%20or%20SAVE%2C%20plan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-borrowers-apply-income-driven-repayment-save-plan-2023-7%5C%22%3Eafter%20it%20began%20beta%20testing%20the%20program%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20press%20release%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20will%20begin%20reaching%20out%20to%20nearly%2030%20million%20student-loan%20borrowers%20to%20invite%20them%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20and%20it%20anticipates%20that%20over%2020%20million%20borrowers%20will%20be%20eligible%20to%20enroll%20in%20the%20plan%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-i-have-to-resume-student-loan-payments-debt-relief-2023-7%5C%22%3Efederal%20student-loan%20payments%20resume%20in%20October%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SAVE%20plan%20is%20a%20sea%20change%20for%20students%2C%20making%20college%20loans%20far%20more%20affordable%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20Education%20James%20Kvaal%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20cut%20payments%20to%20zero%20for%20borrowers%20making%20roughly%20%2415%20an%20hour%2C%20save%20all%20other%20borrowers%20at%20least%20%241%2C000%20a%20year%20compared%20to%20other%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%2C%20and%20stop%20runaway%20interest%20that%20leaves%20folks%20owing%20more%20than%20their%20initial%20loan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SAVE%20plan%20makes%20a%20number%20of%20changes%20to%20existing%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%2C%20which%20are%20intended%20to%20give%20borrowers%20affordable%20monthly%20payments%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20loan%20forgiveness%20after%2020%20or%2025%20years.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20plan%20would%20cut%20payments%20for%20undergraduate%20loans%20in%20half%20and%20stop%20charging%20monthly%20interest%20on%20borrowers'%20balances%20as%20long%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20make%20their%20required%20monthly%20payments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20plan%20would%20ensure%20that%20a%20single%20borrower%20who%20makes%20about%20%2415%20an%20hour%20would%20not%20have%20to%20make%20any%20monthly%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20department%20estimates%20that%20an%20additional%201%20million%20low-income%20borrowers%20would%20experience%20that%20benefit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20can%20now%20apply%20for%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20on%20Federal%20Student%20Aid's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstudentaid.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20department%20says%20takes%20just%20ten%20minutes%20to%20compete.%20The%20application%20also%20allows%20borrowers%20to%20choose%20to%20have%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20access%20their%20income%20each%20year%20so%20they%20do%20not%20have%20to%20recertify%20their%20income%20annually%2C%20preventing%20borrowers%20from%20forgetting%20to%20submit%20the%20required%20paperwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20borrowers%20who%20apply%20for%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20can%20expect%20to%20have%20their%20new%20monthly%20payment%20amount%20for%20their%20first%20payment%20in%20October%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department's%20press%20release%20said.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20borrowers%20apply%2C%20they%20can%20check%20the%20status%20of%20their%20application%20by%20visiting%20their%20account%20dashboard%20on%20StudentAid.gov.%20Borrowers%20who%20are%20currently%20enrolled%20in%20the%20REPAYE%20plan%20will%20automatically%20have%20their%20monthly%20payments%20adjusted%20to%20the%20new%20SAVE%20plan%20before%20payments%20restart.%26quot%3B%3Cu%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20formal%20launch%20of%20the%20application%2C%20the%20department%20also%20announced%20it%20would%20be%20partnering%20with%20groups%20including%20the%20NAACP%20and%20the%20Student%20Debt%20Crisis%20Center%20to%20promote%20outreach%20surrounding%20repayment%20options%2C%20along%20with%20offering%20training%20on%20resources%20borrowers%20can%20use%20as%20they%20reenter%20repayment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SAVE%20plan%20is%20a%20game%20changer%2C%26quot%3B%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20told%20reporters%20on%20a%20Monday%20press%20call.%20%26quot%3BTake%20a%20nurse%20earning%20%2477%2C000%20a%20year%20married%20with%20two%20kids.%20With%20SAVE%2C%20their%20payment%20will%20drop%20from%20%24267%20a%20month%20to%20just%20%2440%20a%20month.%20That's%20over%20%242%2C700%20a%20year%20in%20savings.%20This%20is%20real%20money%20President%20Biden%20is%20putting%20back%20into%20the%20pockets%20of%20working%20families.%20And%20when%20borrowers%20struggle%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20kick%20them%20while%20they're%20down.%20SAVE%20is%20the%20first%20true%20student%20loan%20safety%20net%20in%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20promised%20benefits%20of%20the%20new%20plan%2C%20some%20borrowers%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payments-resume-confusion-borrowers-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Ereported%20difficulties%3C%2Fa%3E%20enrolling%20since%20the%20option%20became%20available%2C%20including%20some%20telling%20Insider%20in%20emails%20that%20their%20new%20monthly%20payment%20estimate%20is%20inaccurate.%20Senior%20administration%20officials%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20press%20call%20that%20they%20believe%20the%20enrollment%20process%20will%20be%20smooth%2C%20and%20an%20Education%20Department%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payments-resume-confusion-borrowers-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20department%20is%20in%20constant%20communication%20with%20student-loan%20servicers%20to%20ensure%20it%20is%20properly%20communicating%20with%20borrowers%20as%20repayment%20resumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20the%20department%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-income-driven-repayment-adjustment-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Estarted%20wiping%20out%20%2439%20billion%20in%20student%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20over%20800%2C000%20borrowers%20on%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20qualifying%2020%20or%2025%20years%20of%20payments.%20The%20department%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20checking%20borrowers'%20accounts%20every%20two%20months%20to%20determine%20who%20qualifies%20for%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-student-loan-repayment-plan-debt-relief-repayment-save-idr-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692707701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6377f3e891af1b0018f3f804%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-student-loan-repayment-plan-debt-relief-repayment-save-idr-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%2020%20million%20student-loan%20borrowers%20are%20expected%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20new%20SAVE%20repayment%20plan%2C%20which%20would%20save%20them%20about%20%241%2C000%20a%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-student-loan-repayment-plan-debt-relief-repayment-save-idr-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prominent%20Russian%20scientist's%20health%20deteriorates%20after%20Luna-25%20lunar%20crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692707692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102949638%2Cimgsize-1686746.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fprominent-russian-scientists-health-deteriorates-after-luna-25-lunar-crash%2Farticleshow%2F102949365