es-increase-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUS%20housing%20affordability%20is%20worse%20today%20than%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20last%20housing%20bubble%2C%26quot%3B%20market%20expert%20Charlie%20Bilello%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ztayeb%40businessinsider.com%20(Zahra%20Tayeb)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-affordability-home-price-us-43-income-mortgage-rates-increase-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20best%20and%20worst%20parts%20of%20being%20an%20NBC%20page%3A%20In%20the%2070s%2C%20I%20worked%20with%20stars%20like%20Regis%20Philbin%20and%20Johnny%20Carson%20and%20was%20paid%20%241.90%20an%20hour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22425%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shelley%20Herman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64de6fc6bd98a60019786443%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22319%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShelley%20Herman%20details%20her%20experience%20working%20as%20an%20NBC%20page%20in%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BMy%20Peacock%20Tale%3A%20Secrets%20of%20an%20NBC%20Page.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EShelley%20Herman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShelley%20Herman%20says%20she%20can%20thank%20Elvis%20Presley%20for%20helping%20her%20get%20her%20start%20at%20NBC%20Studios.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHer%20starting%20pay%20was%20%241.90%20per%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20yet%2C%20she%20would%20do%20pagedom%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20big%20TV%20stars%20started%20as%20pages%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20one%20surefire%20way%20to%20get%20the%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20can%20thank%20Elvis%20Presley%20for%20helping%20me%20get%20my%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20at%20the%20NBC%20Studios%20in%20Burbank%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20happened%3A%20I%20worked%20in%20the%20junior%20clothing%20department%20at%20Sears.%20A%20girl%20I%20worked%20with%20got%20five%20tickets%20to%20see%20Elvis%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20so%20of%20course%2C%20we%20crammed%20into%20my%20Toyota%20for%20a%20road%20trip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20concert%2C%20three%20of%20the%20girls%20I%20arrived%20with%20immediately%20took%20off%20to%20have%20fun%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20and%20I%20was%20left%20with%20Janus%2C%20the%20shy%20wallflower%20who%20got%20us%20the%20Elvis%20tickets.%20We%20sat%20in%20a%20hotel%20coffee%20shop%20eating%20cherry%20pie%20with%20ice%20cream%20and%20talked%20about%20our%20hopes%20and%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20her%20that%20when%20I%20was%20in%20high%20school%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20tickets%20to%20%26quot%3BThe%20Midnight%20Special%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20late-night%20rock%20concert%20show%20that%20was%20taped%20at%20NBC%20Burbank.%20I%20remember%20one%20of%20the%20musicians%20there%20that%20night%20was%20Jim%20Croce.%20While%20sitting%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20watching%20the%20performers%2C%20I%20noticed%20men%20and%20women%20standing%20around%20in%20ugly%20polyester%20uniforms%20who%20not%20only%20got%20to%20listen%20to%20rock%20and%20roll%20music%20for%20free%3B%20they%20were%20getting%20paid%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWow%2C%20I%20want%20that%20job!%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20Janus%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20page%20%E2%80%94%20and%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20her%20mother%20was%20best%20friends%20with%20someone%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20an%20NBC%20page%20two%20weeks%20later%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%201976%20and%20I%20was%2020%2C%20still%20in%20college%20and%20clueless.%20It%20was%20like%20%26quot%3BAlice%20Through%20the%20Looking-Glass%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20instead%2C%20it%20was%20me%20through%20the%20TV%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20its%2090th%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnbc-page-how-i-nailed-lengthy-interview-process-michelle-tokunaga-2022-8%5C%22%3ENBC%20Page%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prestigious%20entry-level%20positions%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry.%20It's%20an%20executive%20recruitment%20and%20training%20program%2C%20but%20some%20of%20the%20all-time%20biggest%20stars%20of%20television%20started%20as%20pages%2C%20including%20Regis%20Philbin%2C%20Gene%20Rayburn%2C%20Chuck%20Barris%2C%20and%2C%20when%20he%20was%20just%2015%20years%20old%2C%20Peter%20Marshall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20I%20could%20tell%20you%20there%20was%20one%20straight%2C%20surefire%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcunicareers.com%2Fpageprogram%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20an%20NBC%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20there%20isn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20become%20an%20NBC%20page%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20candidates%20for%20the%20page%20position%2C%20like%20my%20friend%20Neil%2C%20would%20call%20once%20a%20week%20to%20check%20in%20with%20the%20woman%20who%20ran%20the%20page%20staff%2C%20Eba%20Hawkins.%20He%20was%20attending%20USC%2C%20and%20she%20gave%20him%20the%20job%20when%20he%20graduated.%20She%20admired%20his%20persistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20other%20friend%20Al%20got%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-job-more-selective-than-navy-seals-2016-6%5C%22%3ENBC%20page%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20women%20who%20worked%20behind%20the%20scenes%20on%20%26quot%3BWheel%20of%20Fortune%26quot%3B%20spotted%20him%20as%20a%20contestant%20on%20the%20show.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20Al%20is%20a%20great-looking%20guy%2C%20and%20the%20women%20didn't%20want%20to%20see%20him%20leave.%20So%20they%20encouraged%20him%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20job%2C%20and%20with%20their%20recommendations%2C%20he%20was%20hired%20without%20ever%20really%20knowing%20what%20a%20page%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandy%20had%20a%20similar%20story.%20She%20was%20an%20elementary%20school%20teacher%20when%20she%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20several%20of%20male%20pages%20as%20she%20stood%20in%20line%20to%20see%20%26quot%3BThe%20Tonight%20Show%20Starring%20Johnny%20Carson.%26quot%3B%20They%20even%20helped%20her%20fill%20out%20the%20application%20and%20hand-delivered%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPete%20turned%20down%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20a%20page%20when%20his%20mother%20told%20him%20she%20was%20friends%20with%20the%20network's%20then-president%2C%20Julian%20Goodman.%20He%20wanted%20to%20be%20something%20other%20than%20a%20tour%20guide%20or%20an%20usher.%20He%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20journalist.%20But%20one%20year%20later%2C%20and%20with%20no%20prospects%20in%20sight%2C%20Pete%20dropped%20Goodman's%20name%2C%20and%20wore%20a%20personalized%20button%20on%20his%20blazer%20that%20paraphrased%20the%20lyric%20of%20The%20Beatles'%20song%20%26quot%3BGive%20Peace%20a%20Chance%26quot%3B%20that%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20We%20Are%20Saying%20Is%20Give%20Pete%20a%20Chance%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohnny%20Carson%20was%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20NBC%20tour%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHawkins%20had%20a%20good%20eye%20for%20selecting%20pages%20because%20many%20of%20us%20have%20remained%20close%20friends%20all%20these%20decades%20later.%20A%20core%20group%20of%2015%20of%20us%20still%20get%20together%20about%20once%20a%20month%20to%20celebrate%20birthdays%20and%20weddings%2C%20watch%20award%20shows%2C%20and%20even%20travel%20together.%20When%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20we%20could%20stay%20connected%20through%20Zoom%2C%20and%20friends%20who%20had%20moved%20away%20from%20California%20could%20now%20be%20included%20in%20our%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20hearing%20new%20stories%20about%20our%20time%20touring%20the%20hallways.%20Roxanne%20told%20us%20about%20the%20time%20she%20fainted%20while%20giving%20a%20tour%20and%20was%20surprised%20to%20discover%20TV%20sitcom%20stars%20Don%20Rickles%20and%20Peter%20Isackson%20(from%20the%20show%20%26quot%3BC.P.O.%20Sharkey%26quot%3B)%20were%20carrying%20her%20to%20the%20nurse's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20would%20escort%20celebrities%20to%20press%20events.%20One%20beautiful%2C%20buxom%20blonde%20star%20liked%20to%20have%20something%20%26quot%3Bextra%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20coffee%2C%20and%20it%20was%20Tom's%20job%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20was%20good%20to%20the%20last%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Dinah%20had%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20bartender%20only%20made%20Virgin%20Bloody%20Marys%20for%20her%20boisterous%2C%20barrel-chested%20star.%20When%20he%20found%20out%20they%20didn't%20contain%20alcohol%2C%20Dinah%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BYou've%20been%20drinking%20that%20way%20most%20of%20the%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20of%20the%20tour%20happened%20around%201%3A50%20p.m.%20when%20Johnny%20Carson%20arrived%20at%20the%20studio.%20He%20would%20pull%20into%20the%20number%20one%20space%20on%20the%20lot%20and%20make%20a%20few%20jokes%20with%20the%20group%20who%20just%20happened%20to%20be%20waiting%20near%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20building.%20Johnny%20would%20often%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20tour's%20a%20rip-off.%20Ask%20for%20your%20money%20back.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20whole%20NBC%20tour%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20best%20event%20I%20worked%20on%20was%20the%201977%20Primetime%20Emmy%20Awards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20picked%20up%20comedians%20Sid%20Caesar%20and%20Imogene%20Coca%20in%20a%20limousine%20and%20drove%20with%20them%20to%20the%20Pasadena%20Civic%20Auditorium.%20They%20were%20the%20stars%20of%20%26quot%3BYour%20Show%20of%20Shows%2C%26quot%3B%20a%2090-minute%20live%20show%20much%20like%20Saturday%20Night%20Live%20in%20the%201950s%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20program%20on%20air%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImogene%20bragged%20that%20she%20was%20wearing%20a%20gown%20she%20first%20wore%20in%20the%2050s%2C%20and%20Sid%20wore%20a%20tuxedo.%20They%20looked%20like%20the%20topper%20of%20a%20wedding%20cake.%20She%20was%20talking%20up%20a%20storm%20in%20the%20limo%2C%20and%20Sid%20seemed%20a%20bit%20annoyed.%20I%20loved%20every%20minute%20of%20it.%20It%20was%20my%20own%20private%20%26quot%3BYour%20Show%20of%20Shows!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20night%2C%20just%20as%20they%20finished%20presenting%20an%20Emmy%20award%2C%20the%20entire%20side%20of%20Imogene's%20dress%20busted%20open.%20Sid%20took%20off%20his%20tuxedo%20jacket%20and%20put%20it%20around%20her%20shoulders.%20It%20was%20so%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20that%20wasn't%20enough%20excitement%20for%20me%2C%20I%20also%20helped%20console%20an%20extremely%20teary-eyed%20John%20Travolta%2C%20who%20had%20just%20accepted%20a%20posthumous%20Emmy%20for%20his%20sweetheart%2C%20Diana%20Hyland.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20evening%20ended%20with%20my%20page%20pal%20Jeff%20and%20I%20slowly%20walking%20Alfred%20Hitchcock%20through%20a%20maze%20of%20cables%20in%20a%20dark%20backstage%20area.%20I%20wanted%20to%20say%20something%20to%20Hitchcock%2C%20but%20what%3F%20I%20had%20to%20remain%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHitchcock%20turned%20to%20me%20and%2C%20as%20I%20held%20what%20felt%20like%20half%20his%20body%20weight%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20doing%20a%20very%20good%20job.%26quot%3B%20I%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20my%20senior%20paper%20on%20you.%20Ask%20me%20anything%20about%20you.%26quot%3B%20He%20smiled%20back%20at%20me%20with%20that%20slightly%20wickedly%20wonderful%20Hitchcock%20smile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20an%20NBC%20page%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%20but%20the%20experience%20was%20worth%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20big%20stars%20of%20the%20day%20would%20walk%20the%20hallways%20at%20NBC%20Burbank.%20Redd%20Foxx%20was%20taping%20%26quot%3BSanford%20and%20Son%2C%26quot%3B%20Peter%20Marshall%20was%20hosting%20%26quot%3BHollywood%20Squares%2C%26quot%3B%20Dick%20Clark%20had%20a%20variety%20show%2C%20and%20I%20got%20caught%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20pie%20fight%20Freddie%20Prinze%20Sr.%20was%20having%20next%20to%20Johnny%20Carson's%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20was%20I%20met%20my%20favorite%20musician%20one%20evening%20after%20he%20had%20performed%20on%20The%20Tonight%20Show%2C%20a%20man%20I%20idolized%2C%20Harry%20Chapin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20believed%20when%20applying%20for%20a%20job%2C%20you%20should%20find%20a%20way%20to%20present%20yourself%20in%20a%20way%20so%20people%20will%20want%20to%20meet%20you%2C%20not%20have%20to%20see%20you.%20I%20suggest%20sending%20a%20handwritten%20note%20to%20the%20person%20who%20interviewed%20you%20and%2C%20perhaps%2C%20their%20assistant%20if%20they%20played%20a%20role%20in%20getting%20your%20foot%20in%20the%20door.%20Having%20been%20an%20assistant%2C%20I%20know%20how%20much%20I%20appreciated%20that%20simple%20act%20of%20kindness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20pages%20worked%20long%20hours%20for%20little%20pay%20%E2%80%94%20my%20starting%20pay%20was%20%241.90%20per%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20and%20had%20to%20politely%20deal%20with%20large%20crowds%20who%20weren't%20happy%20waiting%20in%20a%20long%20line%20to%20see%20their%20favorite%20stars.%20Yet%2C%20given%20a%20chance%2C%20most%20of%20my%20colleagues%20and%20I%20agree%2C%20we%20would%20do%20pagedom%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShelley%20Herman%20is%20an%20Emmy-nominated%20show-biz%20veteran%2C%20and%20a%20longtime%20host%2C%20writer%2C%20producer%2C%20and%20personality.%20She%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-60534-20%26h%3D9ca8ed91fa05883911bbb5af38e69b58ae005c713e1fb4e71cc0771931feb66f%26postID%3D64de7264328d007bfe6c12b4%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FMy-Peacock-Tale-Secrets-Page%252Fdp%252FB0C2S7VKPZ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20Peacock%20Tale%3A%20Secrets%20of%20an%20NBC%20Page.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-parts-about-working-as-nbc-page-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692700259000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64de6feabd98a60019786476%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-parts-about-working-as-nbc-page-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20and%20worst%20parts%20of%20the%20NBC%20Page%20program%3A%20what%20is%20was%20like%20working%20for%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prestigious%20entry-level%20positions%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Shelley%20Herman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-parts-about-working-as-nbc-page-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Law%20Raises%20Questions%20About%20Consistency%20With%20Right%20to%20Privacy%20Ruling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F25143729%2Fdata-protection-1200x600.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%20(DPDPA)%2C%202023%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20%E2%80%93%20has%20now%20become%20a%20law.%20It%20received%20presidential%20assent%20on%20August%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20law%20is%20impeded%20by%20several%20fundamental%20flaws%2C%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20fulfilling%20the%20purported%20objectives%20that%20were%20sought%20to%20be%20achieved%20when%20it%20was%20being%20drafted%20as%20a%20data%20protection%20and%20privacy%20law.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20law%20may%20ultimately%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20tool%20through%20which%20the%20government%20will%20be%20able%20to%20circumvent%20the%20already%20scant%20mechanisms%20that%20are%20available%20to%20individuals%20with%20regard%20to%20their%20ability%20to%20exercise%20informational%20autonomy%20and%20ensure%20the%20privacy%20of%20their%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20was%20prepared%20and%20delivered%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20by%20an%20expert%20committee%20headed%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20B.N.%20Srikrishna%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meity.gov.in%2Fwritereaddata%2Ffiles%2FPersonal_Data_Protection_Bill%2C2018.pdf%5C%22%3E2018.%3C%2Fa%3E%20This%20happened%20after%20a%20year%20of%20deliberations%20and%20changes%20since%20the%20need%20for%20a%20privacy%20law%20was%20articulated%20in%20the%20landmark%202017%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-aadhaar-right-to-privacy%5C%22%3Ejudgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgender%2Faadhaar-privacy-judgment-supreme-court-section-377%5C%22%3Eof%20%3Cem%3EJustice%20K.S.%20Puttaswamy%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20the%20ruling%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20held%20privacy%20as%20a%20fundamental%20right%20protected%20under%20Article%2021%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20law%20have%20seen%20several%20deviations%20since%20that%20time.%20However%2C%20the%202018%20draft%20Bill%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20appropriately%20classifying%20data%2C%20affording%20special%20consideration%20to%20protect%20personal%20data%20which%20is%20deemed%20sensitive%20in%20nature.%20The%20most%20recent%20iteration%20of%20the%20law%20however%20does%20not%20make%20a%20distinction%20between%20personal%20data%20and%20sensitive%20personal%20data%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20afford%20any%20additional%20consideration%20to%20adequately%20protect%20such%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fdata-protection-bull-proliferation-digital-india%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Stop%20Data%20Proliferation%20in%20Digital%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20advantages.%20For%20instance%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20personal%20data%20belonging%20to%20or%20identifying%20children%20will%20have%20to%20be%20classified%20separately%2C%20with%20such%20data%20carrying%20a%20greater%20degree%20of%20security%20and%20privacy.%20The%20law%20also%20seeks%20to%20reduce%20the%20rate%20and%20impact%20of%20data%20breaches%20targeting%20Indian%20businesses.%20The%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20law%2C%20however%2C%20goes%20a%20step%20beyond%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fdata-protection-bill-2023-fine-upto-rs-250-crore-on-entities-for-breaching-data-of-citizens-11691109733488.html%5C%22%3Eimposing%20penalties%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20cases%20where%20data%20is%20breached%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20implementation%20of%20adequate%20security%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20said%20that%20the%20law%20isn%E2%80%99t%20balanced%2C%20because%20it%20provides%20wide%20exemptions%20to%20the%20processing%20of%20personal%20data%20to%20the%20government.%20For%20instance%2C%20data%20can%20be%20processed%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20interest%20of%20prevention%2C%20detection%2C%20investigation%20or%20prosecution%20of%20any%20offence%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20These%20kinds%20of%20exemptions%20are%20dangerous%20as%20they%20stand%20to%20legitimise%20widespread%20and%20unwarranted%20collection%20of%20data%20under%20the%20guise%20that%20such%20collection%20and%20processing%20may%20ultimately%20be%20useful%20for%20preventing%20or%20deterring%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20any%20data%20belonging%20to%20any%20person%2C%20at%20any%20time%2C%20may%20potentially%20be%20useful%20in%20the%20future%20indefinitely%20for%20the%20prevention%20or%20detection%20of%20a%20crime%2C%20retrospectively%20or%20otherwise.%20In%20that%20light%2C%20unchecked%20and%20surreptitious%20government%20surveillance%20is%20not%20only%20still%20a%20risk%20with%20the%20DPDPA%2C%20but%20such%20surveillance%20now%20has%20legal%20backing%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20agencies%20will%20have%20significant%20authority%20to%20collect%20and%20retain%20any%20data%20whatsoever%2C%20as%20is%20typically%20the%20case%20with%20exemptions%20relating%20to%20the%20maintenance%20of%20sovereignty%2C%20integrity%2C%20security%20of%20the%20state%2C%20preservation%20of%20public%20order%2C%20prevention%20of%20offences%2C%20and%20incitement%20to%20commit%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20exempts%20processing%20of%20personal%20data%20held%20outside%20of%20India.%20The%20government%20is%20also%20exempt%20from%20being%20required%20to%20delete%20any%20data%20that%20it%20possesses%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20purpose%20it%20may%20have%20been%20collected%20for%2C%20on%20the%20request%20of%20an%20individual%2C%20or%20by%20way%20of%20a%20prescribed%20data%20retention%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20not%20bound%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuk.practicallaw.thomsonreuters.com%2FGlossary%2FUKPracticalLaw%2FI1a11102e5ea511e89bf199c0ee06c731%3FtransitionType%3DDefault%26contextData%3D(sc.Default)%26firstPage%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Epurpose%20limitations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edata%20collected%20for%20one%20specified%20purpose%20be%20used%20for%20a%20new%2C%20incompatible%20purpose%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20which%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20regulations%20imposed%20on%20businesses.%20However%2C%20certain%20types%20of%20data%2C%20particularly%20sensitive%20personal%20data%2C%20would%20legitimately%20warrant%20prescribed%20retention%20periods.%20It%E2%80%99s%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20law%20does%20not%20prioritise%20one%20category%20of%20data%20over%20another%2C%20except%20in%20cases%20involving%20data%20related%20to%20or%20concerning%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdigital-personal-data-protection-bill-adverse-impact-press-freedom-editors-guild%5C%22%3EDigital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20Could%20Have%20Adverse%20Impact%20on%20Press%20Freedom%2C%20Say%20Editors%20Guild%20and%20Digipub%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20exemptions%20for%20the%20government%20relate%20to%20data%20deemed%20%E2%80%9Cnecessary%20for%20research%2C%20archiving%20or%20statistical%20purposes%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%E2%80%9D%20as%20long%20as%20such%20data%20is%20not%20used%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20for%20the%20persons%20whom%20the%20data%20identifies.%20This%20may%20seem%20an%20agreeable%20exemption%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20ones%20described%20above%2C%20but%20exemptions%20for%20purposes%20such%20as%20research%20or%20archival%20are%20overly%20broad%2C%20and%20may%20still%20violate%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20summation%2C%20the%20Act%20conflates%20the%20concept%20of%20informational%20privacy%20and%20leaves%20much%20to%20be%20desired%20as%20it%20substitutes%20information%20security%20with%20the%20ability%20of%20an%20individual%20to%20exercise%20autonomy%20over%20the%20privacy%20of%20their%20data.%20The%20enactment%20of%20the%20DPDPA%20in%20this%20state%20appears%20to%20deviate%20from%20the%20original%20vision%20of%20what%20the%20law%20could%20have%20been%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20need%20for%20such%20legislation%20was%20first%20articulated%20in%20the%20Right%20to%20Privacy%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C