20three%20steel%20boxes%2C%20a%20smartphone%20connected%20with%20a%20Phone%20pay%20QR%20code%20and%20Rs%20640%20cash%20in%20the%20boxes.%20Prakash%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20booked%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20begging%20act%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20SHO%20Film%20Nagar%20for%20further%20action.%20The%20police%20said%20the%20babies%20were%20fed%20toddy%20to%20make%20them%20unwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrakash's%20income%20was%20not%20sufficient%20and%20he%20hatched%20a%20plan%20and%20hired%20minor%20boys%20from%20nearby%20slums%20for%20organised%20Part%20Time%20Begging%20at%20Film%20Nagar%20Bus%20stop%20and%20nearby%20shopping%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakash%20used%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20steel%20boxes%20to%20the%20minor%20boys%20and%20also%20pasted%20QR%20codes%20on%20the%20boxes%20(which%20were%20linked%20to%20his%20account)%20for%20begging.%20The%20man%20used%20to%20hand%20over%20Rs%20200%20per%20day%20to%20them%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterrogations%20by%20task%20force%20personnel%20unveiled%20that%20the%20beggars%20were%20earning%20ranging%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20Rs%202000%20every%20day.%20Prakash%20was%20said%20to%20be%20making%20as%20much%20as%20Rs%206000%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hyderabad%20Police%20busted%20another%20begging%20gang.%20The%20Hyderabad%20Commissioner's%20Task%20Force%20South-East%20Zone%20team%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Malakpet%20police%2C%20caught%20a%20begging%20mafia%20gang%20who%20were%20cheating%20and%20seeking%20money%20from%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20charity.%20The%20police%20arrested%2010%20people%20including%20three%20organisers%20and%20seven%20beggars.%20The%20police%20also%20seized%20two%20auto-rickshaws%2C%20Rs%201.38%20lakh%20and%20some%20documents%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20in%20a%20release%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20were%20cheating%20the%20public%20by%20begging%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20charity%20name