s%20for%20academic%20freedom%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20has%20begun%20looking%C2%A0%20into%20the%20scholarly%20paper%20by%20a%20former%20Ashoka%20University%20professor%20on%20%E2%80%98Democratic%20Backsliding%20in%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20and%20is%20seeking%20to%20interview%20the%20author%20and%20faculty%20members%20of%20the%20economics%20department%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIB%20officials%20visited%20the%20private%20university%20on%20Monday%20armed%20with%20newspaper%20cuttings%20seeking%20to%20meet%20the%20author%20of%20the%20paper%2C%20Sabyasachi%20Das%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20Pune.%20A%20suggestion%20that%20other%20members%20of%20the%20faculty%20meet%20with%20them%20to%20discuss%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20paper%20found%20no%20takers%20as%20the%20officials%20refused%20to%20convey%20their%20request%20for%20information%20in%20writing.%20They%20then%20left%20after%20saying%20they%20would%20return%20to%20the%20campus%20again%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20not%20have%20confirmed%20information%20about%20the%20status%20of%20the%20second%20planned%20visit%20and%20will%20update%20this%20story%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDas%E2%80%99s%20paper%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4512936%5C%22%3Epublished%20online%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20uses%20advanced%20econometric%20techniques%20to%20generate%20estimates%20of%20how%20many%20of%20the%20marginal%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20general%20election%20that%20the%20BJP%20won%20might%20have%20been%20due%20to%20some%20form%20of%20%E2%80%98manipulation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20set%20off%20a%20political%20controversy%2C%20with%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20denouncing%20Das%E2%80%99s%20research.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learned%20that%20some%20of%20the%20businessmen%20who%20invested%20in%20Ashoka%20and%20sit%2