ood%2Fnews%2Fsuniel-shetty-wishes-wife-mana-a-happy-birthday-with-an-unseen-pic-kids-athiya-and-ahan-also-chip-in-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F102941657.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20%26quot%3BBiggest%20Asset%26quot%3B%20In%20Pakistan%20Is...%3A%20Congress's%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBatting%20for%20resumption%20of%20dialogue%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20diplomat-turned-politician%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20says%20India%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20take%20its%20due%20place%20in%20the%20world%20as%20long%20as%20its%20western%20neighbour%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Balbatross%20around%20our%20necks''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%2C%20who%20served%20as%20India's%20consul%20general%20in%20Karachi%20from%20December%201978-January%201982%2C%20has%20dedicated%20a%20full%20chapter%20to%20his%20Pakistan%20stint%20in%20his%20autobiography%20%26quot%3BMemoirs%20of%20a%20Maverick%20--%20The%20First%20Fifty%20Years%20(1941-1991)%26quot%3B%20that%20hit%20the%20stands%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20on%20his%20new%20book%2C%20published%20by%20Juggernaut%20Books%2C%20Mr%20Aiyar%20said%20the%20high%20point%20of%20his%20bureaucratic%20career%20was%20undoubtedly%20his%20stint%20as%20consul%20general%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20he%20has%20dwelt%20at%20very%20great%20length%20on%20his%20three%20years%20in%20Karachi%20in%20the%20first%20volume%20out%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20asset%26quot%3B%20in%20Pakistan%20were%20the%20people%20there%20who%20did%20not%20consider%20it%20an%20enemy%20country%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20coming%20back%20from%20a%20dinner%20one%20day%2C%20within%20the%20first%20two-three%20weeks%20of%20the%20posting%2C%20when%20my%20wife%20Suneet%20asked%20me%20a%20question%20that%20reverberated%20in%20my%20mind%20in%20my%20stay%20in%20Karachi%20-%20'This%20is%20an%20enemy%20country%2C%20right'%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Aiyar%20said%20he%20asked%20himself%20the%20question%20through%20his%20three%20years%20there%20and%20for%20the%20last%2040%20years%20since%20he%20came%20back%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20whatever%20may%20be%20the%20view%20of%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20army%2C%20or%20sections%20of%20polity%2C%20as%20far%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20are%20concerned%2C%20they%20are%20neither%20an%20enemy%20country%20nor%20do%20they%20regard%20India%20as%20an%20enemy%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed%20in%20his%20interview%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20we%20want%20to%20display%20our%20disapproval%20of%20the%20(Pakistani)%20government%2C%20visas%20are%20stopped%2C%20films%20are%20stopped%2C%20TV%20exchanges%20are%20stopped%2C%20books%20are%20stopped%2C%20travel%20is%20stopped%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20see%20why%20we%20do%20not%20know%20how%20to%20leverage%20the%20goodwill%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20our%20diplomatic%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Aiyar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20all%20dialogue%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20frozen%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20Mr%20(Narendra)%20Modi%20became%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%2C%20almost%20every%20prime%20minister%2C%20if%20he%20had%20the%20time%2C%20was%20attempting%20some%20kind%20of%20a%20dialogue%20with%20the%20Pakistanis%20but%20now%20we%20are%20in%20a%20freeze%20and%20the%20victims%20of%20this%20freeze%20are%20not%20the%20army%20of%20Pakistan%20which%20is%20still%20swigging%20its%20scotch%2C%20it%20is%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20whose%20relatives%20in%20large%20numbers%20live%20in%20India%20and%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20a%20desire%20to%20visit%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Aiyar%20said%20that%20during%20his%20diplomatic%20stint%20in%20Karachi%2C%20he%20issued%20three%20lakh%20visas%20and%20did%20not%20get%20a%20single%20complaint%20of%20misuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20why%20are%20we%20targeting%20the%20Pakistani%20people%3F%20You%20can%20target%20the%20Pakistani%20establishment%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20but%20as%20far%20as%20the%20people%20are%20concerned%2C%20they%20are%20our%20biggest%20asset%20and%20as%20far%20as%20the%20establishment%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20can%20target%20them%20but%20we%20need%20to%20engage%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20diplomat%2C%20who%20quit%20the%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20in%201989%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20impressed%20by%20a%20book%20launch%20event%20recently%20where%20five%20former%20Indian%20high%20commissioners%20to%20Pakistan%20participated%20and%20all%20insisted%20that%20dialogue%20with%20Islamabad%20was%20important%20and%20there%20can%20be%20no%20progress%20without%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20who%20clearly%20showed%20that%20if%20you%20do%20talk%20to%20the%20Pakistanis%20perhaps%20out%20of%20the%20public%20eye%20in%20an%20uninterrupted%20and%20uninterruptible%20way%2C%20you%20can%20resolve%20even%20the%20issue%20of%20Kashmir.%20After%20all%2C%20there%20was%20a%20four-point%20agreement%20that%20had%20been%20drafted%20and%20virtually%20agreed%20upon%20and%20it%20was%20not%20because%20the%20Pakistanis%20withdrew%20from%20that%20four-point%20agreement%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20because%20the%20government%20of%20(Pervez)%20Musharraf%20fell%20into%20difficulty%20and%20eventually%20fell%20that%20the%20dialogue%20was%20interrupted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20any%20dialogue%20with%20Pakistan%20is%20going%20to%20suffer%20setbacks%2C%20is%20going%20to%20take%20time%20and%20we%20need%20to%20have%20the%20patience%20and%20persistence%2C%20to%20establish%20a%20viable%20relationship%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20long%20as%20Pakistan%20is%20an%20albatross%20around%20our%20necks%2C%20we%20just%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20take%20our%20due%20place%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20ludicrous%20to%20suggest%20that%20India%20is%20the%20'vishwaguru'%20when%20we%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20our%20neighbour%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Aiyar%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Aiyar%20makes%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20good%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20in%20the%20book%20as%20well%2C%20saying%20common%20Pakistanis%20not%20only%20speak%20the%20same%20language%20as%20us%20and%20share%20much%20of%20the%20same%20'tehzeeb'%20(culture)%2C%20they%20love%20Bollywood%20and%20its%20music%20and%20laugh%20at%20the%20same%20jokes%20and%20befriend%20us%20everywhere%20outside%20the%20subcontinent.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692697260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2F6icdgopg_mani-shankar-aiyar_625x300_14_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-wont-take-its-due-place-in-world-till-pakistan-is-congresss-mani-shankar-aiyar-4318429%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Batting%20for%20resumption%20of%20dialogue%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20diplomat-turned-politician%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20says%20India%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20take%20its%20due%20place%20in%20the%20world%20as%20long%20as%20its%20western%20neighbour%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Balbatross%20around%20our%20necks''.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-wont-take-its-due-place-in-world-till-pakistan-is-congresss-mani-shankar-aiyar-4318429%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%