0form%20the%20nucleus%20of%20the%2015-member%20World%20Cup%20side.%20Leg-spinner%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20was%20a%20notable%20omission%20from%20the%20squad%2C%20leaving%20India%20with%20only%20one%20wrist%20spinner%20in%20Kuldeep%20Yadav.%20Axar%20Patel%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20are%20the%20other%20spin%20bowling%20options%20in%20the%20squad%20that%20was%20named%20on%20Monday.%20Few%20also%20wondered%20why%20senior%20off-spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20very%20useful%20batter%20lower%20down%20the%20order%2C%20was%20not%20picked%20in%20the%20side.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20players%20who%20will%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20lucky.%20But%20the%20team%20is%20selected.%20So%20don't%20talk%20about%20Ashwin.%20Stop%20creating%20controversy.%20This%20is%20our%20team%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20like%20it%2C%20don't%20watch%20the%20matches%20but%20stop%20saying%20that%20he%20should%20have%20been%20picked%20or%20another%20should%20be%20there%2C%20this%20is%20a%20wrong%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20'Aaj%20Tak'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Jadeja%20and%20Axar%20have%20also%20proved%20their%20batting%20abilities%20across%20formats%20and%20will%20add%20depth%20to%20India's%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20L%20Rahul%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20were%20also%20named%20in%20the%20team%20for%20the%20tournament%20beginning%20August%2031%20while%20highly-rated%20young%20batter%20Tilak%20Varma%20earned%20a%20maiden%20call-up%20to%20the%20one-day%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20believed%20the%20team%20selection%20was%20fair%20and%20expressed%20optimism%20ahead%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20absolutely%20(this%20team%20can%20win%20the%20World%20Cup).%20Who%20else%20would%20you%20have%20picked%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20player%20can%20claim%20that%20there%20has%20been%20an%20injustice%20to%20him.%20The%20experienced%20and%20in-form%20players%20have%20been%20selected%20in%20the%2017-member%20Asia%20Cup%20squad%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20also%20backed%20the%20decision%20to%20pick%20Rahul%2C%20who%20has%20developed%20a%20new%20niggle%20and%20might%20not%20be%20available%20for%20the%20first%20match%20of%20the%20continental%20tournament%20against%20Pakistan%20on%20September%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20see%20what%20his%20injury%20is%20like.%20Winning%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20important%20but%20the%20goal%20is%20the%20World%20Cup.%20So%20if%20the%20team%20management%20wants%20KL%20Rahul%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20squad%20then%20I%20think%20it's%20right%20that%20they%20have%20selected%20him%20for%20Asia%20Cup%20despite%20a%20niggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20India%20are%20concerned%2C%20there%20are%2011%20days%20to%20go.%20That's%20enough%20time%20to%20recover%20from%20a%20niggle.%20And%20there%20are%20more%20matches%20as%20well%2C%20right%20till%20the%20middle%20of%20September.%20I%20think%20it%20will%20be%20fair%20to%20give%20KL%20Rahul%20(a%20chance)%20after%20all%20that%20he%20has%20done%20for%20India%20in%20the%20past%2C%20to%20give%20him%20the%20opportunity%20to%20recover%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20team's%20chances%20of%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20Gavaskar%20said%20it's%20a%20good%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20team%20that%20has%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20a%20good%20team.%20We%20should%20have%20the%2015%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20from%20this%20team%20only.%20When%20you%20play%20for%20India%2C%20every%20match%20is%20important.%20You%20should%20always%20strive%20to%20win%20every%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20a%20big%20tournament.%20But%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20is%20totally%20different%2C%20that%20can't%20be%20replicated%20by%20an%20Asia%20Cup%20win.%20So%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20bigger%20picture.%20If%20they%20win%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20very%20good%20but%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692696780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-03%2Fdp5fg9d_sunil-gavaskar-bcci_625x300_05_March_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fdont-think-any-player-sunil-gavaskars-injustice-take-on-indias-asia-cup-2023-squad-4318631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20had%20an%20interesting%20comment%20regarding%20India's%20squad%20for%20Asia%20Cup%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fdont-think-any-player-sunil-gavaskars-injustice-take-on-indias-asia-cup-2023-squad-4318631%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fdont-think-any-player-sunil-gavaskars-injustice-take-on-indias-asia-cup-2023-squad-4318631%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fdont-think-any-player-sunil-gavaskars-injustice-take-on-indias-asia-cup-2023-squad-4318631%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%3A%20Isro%20releases%20new%20images%20of%20moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692696665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102941275%2Cimgsize-849267.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchandrayaan-3-isro-releases-new-images-of-moon-captured-from-by-lander-camera%2Farticleshow%2F102941147.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(Isro)%20on%20Tuesday%20released%20images%20of%20the%20Moon%20captured%20by%20the%20Lander%20Imager%20Camera%204%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20on%20August%2020.%20%26quot%3BThe%20moon%20as%20captured%20by%20the%20Lander%20Imager%20Camera%204%20on%20August%2020%2C%20