0they%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20ED%20had%20proceeded%20with%20its%20investigation%20in%20this%20case%20despite%20being%20restrained%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20from%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F08%2F07%2Flgd27-sc-liquor-scam-chhattisgarh.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20asked%20the%20ED%20on%20July%2018%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstay%20%5Bits%5D%20hand%20in%20all%20manner%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20case%20after%20taking%20note%20of%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20contention%20that%20a%20certain%20prerequisite%20for%20the%20ED%20to%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20an%20investigation%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20court%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20or%20anywhere%20else%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98predicate%E2%80%99%20or%20primary%20offence%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20such%20an%20offence%20that%20enables%20the%20ED%2C%20a%20federal%20financial%20crimes%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftracking-the-ed-case-by-case-puzzling-questions-emerge-in-its-handling-of-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3Eto%20carry%20out%20a%20separate%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%20so%20far%20has%20been%20on%20alleged%20offences%20under%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%201961%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20predicate%20offence%20under%20the%20PMLA%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flivelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fed-cannot-be-a-law-unto-itself-supreme-court-extends-interim-relief-in-chhattisgarh-liquor-scam-case-235805%5C%22%3Elegal%20news%20website%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20being%20asked%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstay%20its%20hand%E2%80%9D%20on%20July%2018%2C%20the%20ED%20wrote%20to%20the%20UP%20government%20ten%20days%20later%20regarding%20the%20alleged%20manufacture%20of%20fake%20holograms%20used%20in%20the%20liquor%20scam%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-restrains-enforcement-directorate-in-fresh-liquor-syndicate-case-says-ed-cannot-be-a-law-unto-itself-101692641360075.html%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20police%20then%20filed%20an%20FIR%20in%20this%20matter%20against%20three%20people%2C%20including%20Anil%20Tuteja%2C%20on%20July%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20different%20accused%20in%20this%20FIR%2C%20who%20is%20a%20special%20secretary%20in%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Excise%20Department%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20arguments%20that%20the%20ED%20was%20trying%20to%20circumvent%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20by%20writing%20to%20the%20UP%20police%2C%20the%20ED%20argued%20in%20the%20top%20court%20on%20August%207%20that%20it%20was%20bound%20to%20inform%20police%20about%20any%20offence%20it%20detects%20in%20the%20course%20of%20its%20investigation%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftracking-the-ed-case-by-case-puzzling-questions-emerge-in-its-handling-of-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3ETracking%20the%20ED%20Case%20by%20Case%2C%20Puzzling%20Questions%20Emerge%20in%20Its%20Handling%20of%20Opposition%20Leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%20to%20say%20that%20Justices%20Kaul%20and%20Dhulia%20asked%20the%20ED%20whether%20it%20learned%20of%20the%20fake%20hologram%20developments%20before%20or%20after%20the%20July%2018%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20our%20query%20as%20to%20when%20these%20aspects%20came%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20ED%2C%20learned%20%5Badditional%20solicitor%20general%5D%20se