3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bhatia%20explains%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20key%20concern%20in%20the%20Anoop%20Baranwal%20case%20was%20that%20the%20mechanism%20to%20appoint%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioners%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20must%20secure%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20That%20can%20only%20be%20done%20by%20a%20non-partisan%20or%20multi-partisan%20appointment%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20not%20happen%20if%20the%20mechanism%20is%20dominated%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20another%20minister%20appointed%20by%20the%20PM.%20Equally%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20essential%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20should%20be%20part%20of%20the%20mechanism.%20That%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20in%20India%20has%20so%20far%20focused%20on%20the%20exclusion%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20from%20the%20appointment%20mechanism%20rather%20than%20on%20the%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20mechanism%20is%20independent%20of%20the%20government%20and%20not%20influenced%20by%20it.%20Only%20then%20can%20the%20mechanism%20ensure%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatia%20discusses%20what%20happens%20in%20other%20major%20parliamentary%20democracies%20and%20whether%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20Search%20Committee%20to%20put%20forward%20a%20panel%20of%20five%20candidates%20to%20the%20selection%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20PM%20alleviates%20the%20concerns%20that%20have%20been%20raised.%20He%20discusses%20two%20points%20made%20by%20former%20CEC%20S.%20Y.%20Quraishi.%20First%2C%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20in%20the%20appointing%20panel%20could%20create%20problems%20if%20there%20is%20a%20challenge%20because%20it%20would%20then%20automatically%20go%20to%20him%20and%20create%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20Second%2C%20if%20the%20government%20refuses%20to%20change%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20appointing%20panel%20should%20the%20selection%20be%20unanimous%20rather%20than%20based%20on%20majority%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatia%20discusses%20the%20possibility%20of%20this%20Bill%2C%20if%20it%20is%20passed%2C%20being%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20also%20discusses%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20act%20expeditiously%20if%20there%20is%20a%20challenge%20rather%20than%20delay%20matters%20for%20years%2C%20as%20happened%20with%20Article%20370%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Bhatia%20discusses%20the%20political%20morality%20of%20a%20government%20attempting%20to%20blatantly%20defy%20the%20spirit%20of%20democracy%20by%20dominating%20the%20appointing%20panel%20for%20CECs%20and%20ECs.%20What%20does%20this%20reveal%20of%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20PM%20and%20his%20government%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20fair%20play%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWatch%20the%20full%20interview%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_BbrnLupDm4%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692695747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22143854%2FKT-22-Aug.00_25_18_25.Still006.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fvideo-karan-thapar-election-commission-gautam-bhatia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Legal%20scholar%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20says%20the%20key%20concern%20is%20not%20whether%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20is%20part%20of%20the%20panel%20that%20appoints%20the%20CEC%20and%20EC%20but%20that%20the%20process%20must%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fvideo-karan-thapar-election-commission-gautam-bhatia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Rakhi%20told%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20like%20Sana%20Khan%2C%20wear%20abaya%20and%20do%20namaz'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692695417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102940355%2Cimgsize-36250.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fadil-khan-durrani-rakhi-sawant-told-me-i-want-to-become-like-sana-khan-wear-abaya-and-do-namaz%2Farticleshow%2F102940355.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adil%20Khan%20Durrani%20made%20several%20claims%20against%20Rakhi%20Sawant%20in%20the%20press%20conference%20that%20he%20held%20on%20Monday%20(August%2021).%20He%20said%20that%20it%20was%20Rakhi's%20choice%20to%20convert%20to%20Islam%20and%20follow%20it%20to%20the%20tee%20to%20be%20accepted%20by%20his%20family.%20He%20also%20talked%20about%20their%20marriage%2C%20her%20ex-Ritesh%20Singh%2C%20and%20the%20false%20accusations%20made%20by%20her%20against%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fadil-khan-durrani-rakhi-sawant-told-me-i-want-to-become-like-sana-khan-wear-abaya-and-do-namaz%2Farticleshow%2F102940355.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Did%20Viral%20Red-Roofed%20House%20Survive%20Hawaii%20Wildfires%3F%20Owner%20Explains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20devastating%20wildfires%20in%20Hawaii's%20Maui%20caused%20widespread%20devastation%2C%20burning%20down%20almost%20every%20property.%20But%20one%20house%20remains%20untouched.%20Photos%20of%20the%20two-storey%20house%20with%20white%20walls%20and%20red%20roof%20went%20viral%20amid%20the%20apocalyptic%20devastation%20surrounding%20it.%20The%20home's%20garden%20also%20appears%20to%20have%20kept%20its%20greenery%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20ashes%20and%20charred%20trees.%20The%20miracle%20has%20left%20social%20media%20abuzz%2C%20with%20many%20users%20asking%20how%20it's%20possible.%20The%20house's%20owner%20has%20now%20opened%20up%20what%20she%20thinks%20helps%20it%20survive%20last%20week's%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20100%25%20wood%20house%20so%20it's%20not%20like%20we%20fireproofed%20it%20or%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Dora%20Atwater%20Millikin%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-08-18%2Fhow-did-the-red-house-survive-the-lahaina-fire%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Atwater%20Millikin%20and%20her%20husband%20Dudley%20recently%20renovated%20the%20100-year-old%20house%2C%20which%20they%20have%20owned%20for%20three%20years%2C%20without%20thinking%20about%20the%20wildfires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20love%20old%20buildings%2C%20so%20we%20just%20wanted%20to%20honor%20the%20building.%20And%20we%20didn't%20change%20the%20building%20in%20any%20way%20-%20we%20just%20restored%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Atwater%20Millikin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20one%20decision%20that%20helped%20the%20house%20escape%20a%20devastating%20fate%20was%20the%20couple's%20decision%20to%20replace%20the%20asphalt%20roof%20with%20one%20made%20out%20of%20heavy-gauge%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20fire%2C%20there%20were%20pieces%20of%20wood%20-%206%2C%2012%20inches%20long%20-%20that%20were%20on%20fire%20and%20just%20almost%20floating%20through%20the%20air%20with%20the%20wind%20and%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Atwater%20Millikin%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20would%20hit%20people's%20roofs%2C%20and%20if%20it%20was%20an%20asphalt%20roof%2C%20it%20would%20catch%20on%20fire.%20And%20otherwise%2C%20they%20would%20fall%20off%20the%20roof%20and%20then%20ignite%20the%20foliage%20around%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foliage%20around%20the%20house%20was%20also%20cut%20down%20and%20stones%20added%20to%20the%20ground%20surrounding%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20red-roofed%20house%20was%20not%20too%20close%20to%20neighbouring%20properties%2C%20instead%20shared%20border%20with%20the%20ocean%2C%20a%20road%20and%20an%20empty%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ms%20Atwater%20Millikin%20and%20her%20husband%20plan%20to%20return%20to%20Maui%20soon%20and%20open%20their%20place%20to%20neighbours%20who%20were%20left%20homeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692695160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fio3eh97o_hawaii-wildfire-house-survives-afp-1200_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20images%20of%20the%20two-storey%20house%20in%20Hawaii%20were%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Children%20and%20teachers%20trapped%20in%20chairlift%20dangling%20274m%20above%20Pakistan%20canyon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F70x70%2Fskynews-pakistan-chair-lift_6259111.jpg%3F20230822131005%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpakistan-six-children-and-two-adults-trapped-in-chairlift-dangling-350m-above-canyon-12945005%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20risky%26quot%3B%20rescue%20effort%20is%20under%20way%20to%20save%20six%20children%20and%20two%20teachers%20who%20are%20trapped%20in%20a%20chairlift%20dangling%20274m%20(900ft)%20over%20a%20canyon%20in%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A201%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpakistan-six-children-and-two-adults-trapped-in-chairlift-dangling-350m-above-canyon-12945005%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpakistan-six-children-and-two-adults-trapped-in-chairlift-dangling-350m-above-canyon-12945005%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpakistan-six-children-and-two-adults-trapped-in-chairlift-dangling-350m-above-canyon-12945005%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women%20Engaging%20in%20'Legal%20Terrorism'%20By%20'Misusing'%20Section%20on%20Cruelty%20By%20Husbands%3A%20Calcutta%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F13112951%2FCalcutta_High_Court_-_Kolkata_2011-12-18_0328-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20on%20Monday%20(August%2021)%20said%20that%20women%20are%20engaging%20in%20%E2%80%9Clegal%20terrorism%E2%80%9D%20by%20misusing%20Section%20498A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20section%20criminalises%20cruelty%20against%20a%20woman%20by%20her%20husband%20or%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingle-judge%20Justice%20Subhendu%20Samanta%20said%20that%20though%20the%20section%20was%20brought%20it%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20welfare%2C%20it%20is%20now%20being%20%E2%80%9Cmisused%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20legislature%20has%20enacted%20the%20provision%20of%20Section%20498A%20to%20strike%20out%20the%20dowry%20menace%20from%20the%20society.%20But%20it%20is%20observed%20in%20several%20cases%20that%20by%20misusing%20of%20said%20provision%20new%20legal%20terrorism%20is%20unleashed%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwomen-unleashed-legal-terrorism-misusing-section-498a-ipc-calcutta-high-court%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20the%20judge%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20criminal%20law%20allows%20a%20complainant%20to%20file%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20but%20the%20same%20has%20to%20be%20justified%20by%20adducing%20cogent%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20quashing%20charges%20under%20Section%20489A%20against%20a%20man%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20specific%20case%2C%20the%20judge%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20a%20man%20and%20his%20family%20members%20challenging%20the%20criminal%20cases%20lodged%20against%20them%20by%20his%20estranged%20wife%20in%20October%20and%20December%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20direct%20allegation%20against%20the%20husband%20by%20the%20de-facto%20complainant%20is%20merely%20from%20her%20version.%20It%20support%20no%20documentary%20or%20medical%20evidence.%20One%20neighbour%20has%20heard%20about%20the%20quarrel%20of%20the%20wife%20and%20her%20husband%3B%20the%20quarrel%20of%20two%20persons%20does%20not%20mean%20or%20prove%20who%20is%20in%20aggression%20or%20who%20is%20aggrieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20of%20a%20view%20that%20the%20instant%20criminal%20proceedings%20initiated%20by%20the%20de-facto%20complainant%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20in-laws%20does%20not%20disclose%20prima%20facie%20offence%20against%20them%20as%20alleged.%20The%20proceeding%20are%20instituted%20only%20to%20fulfil%20personal%20grudge.%20Considering%20the%20circumstances%20I%20think%20it%20necessary%20to%20invoke%20the%20inherent%20power%20of%20this%20court%20to%20quash%20the%20proceedings%20otherwise%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%20would%20be%20tantamount%20to%20the%20abuse%20of%20process%20of%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F13112951%2FCalcutta_High_Court_-_Kolkata_2011-12-18_0328-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwomen-engaging-in-legal-terrorism-by-misusing-section-on-cruelty-by-husbands-calcutta-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Single-judge%20Justice%20Subhendu%20Samanta%20said%20that%20though%20the%20section%20was%20brought%20it%20for%20women's%20welfare%2C%20it%20is%20now%20being%20%26quot%3Bmisused%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Breakthrough%20for%20studying%20ancient%20life%20as%20DNA%20extracted%20from%202%2C900-year-old%20palace%20brick%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-clay-brick-history_6258855.jpg%3F20230822093412%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ancient%20DNA%20has%20been%20extracted%20from%20a%202%2C900-year-old%20clay%20brick%2C%20potentially%20unlocking%20new%20ways%20of%20studying%20life%20from%20generations%20gone%20by.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2-900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2-900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fancient-dna-extracted-from-2-900-year-old-clay-palace-brick-time-capsule-for-first-time-12944952%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chess%20World%20Cup%20Final%3A%20A%20Look%20At%20Praggnanandhaa's%20Record%20Against%20Carlsen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ER%20Praggnanandhaa%20impressed%20everyone%20by%20becoming%20the%20second%20Indian%20chess%20player%20ever%20in%20history%20after%20the%20legendary%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20to%20reach%20the%20final%20of%20Chess%20World%20Cup.%20He%20defeated%20Fabiano%20Caruana%203.5-2.5%20in%20a%20tight%20semi-final%20clash%20to%20set%20up%20his%20match%20against%20five-time%20world%20champion%20Magnus%20Carlsen.%20While%20Praggnanandhaa%20has%20been%20quite%20impressive%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20facing%20a%20renowned%20player%20like%20Carlsen%20is%20always%20massive.%20The%20Norwegian%20grandmaster%20is%20a%20former%20five-time%20World%20Chess%20Champion%20and%20current%20four-time%20World%20Rapid%20Chess%20Champion%20and%20current%20six-time%20World%20Blitz%20Chess%20Champion.%20He%20claimed%20the%20top%20rank%20in%20the%20FIDE%20world%20chess%20rankings%20back%20in%202011%20and%20only%20Garry%20Kasparov%20has%20spent%20more%20time%20as%20the%20top%20player%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarlsen%20and%20Praggnanandhaa%20have%20faced%20each%20other%20a%20total%20of%2019%20times%20across%20various%20competitions%20with%20the%20World%20No.%201%20enjoying%20the%20slightest%20of%20edges.%20In%20classical%20chess%2C%20they%20have%20played%20one%20game%20against%20each%20other%20and%20it%20ended%20in%20a%20draw.%20In%20Rapid%2FExhibition%20games%2C%20Carlsen%20holds%20a%207-5%20win%20advantage%20with%20six%20games%20finishing%20in%20a%20draw.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20unwise%20to%20say%20that%20the%20more%20experienced%20player%20holds%20the%20edge%20but%20it%20is%20the%20recent%20results%20that%20will%20give%20Praggnanandhaa%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018-year-old%20became%20the%20youngest%20person%20to%20defeat%20Carlsen%20since%20he%20became%20world%20champion%20in%202013.%20The%20historic%20victory%20came%20in%20in%20February%202022%20at%20the%20Airthings%20Masters%20(an%20online%20rapid%20chess%20tournament).%20Cut%20to%20May%202022%20and%20the%20youngster%20was%20once%20again%20the%20victor%20against%20Carlsen%20at%20the%20Chessable%20Masters%20online%20rapid%20chess%20tournament%20%E2%80%93%20a%20win%20that%20earned%20him%20a%20lot%20of%20praise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20biggest%20achievement%20for%20Praggnanandhaa%20came%20exactly%20one%20year%20ago%20when%20he%20defeated%20Carlsen%20in%20three%20consecutive%20games%20%E2%80%94%20one%20rapid%20and%20two%20blitz%20%E2%80%94%20at%202022%20FTX%20Crypto%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F3seo64s8_edfwe_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fchess-world-cup-final-a-look-at-r-praggnanandhaas-record-against-magnus-carlsen-4318628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R%20Praggnanandhaa%20faces%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20Chess%20World%20Cup%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fchess-world-cup-final-a-look-at-r-praggnanandhaas-record-against-magnus-carlsen-4318628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fchess-world-cup-final-a-look-at-r-praggnanandhaas-record-against-magnus-carlsen-4318628%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fchess-world-cup-final-a-look-at-r-praggnanandhaas-record-against-magnus-carlsen-4318628%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-Origin%20Ex-Minister%20In%20Final%203-Way%20Race%20To%20Be%20Singapore%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESingapore-born%20Indian-origin%20Tharman%20Shanmugaratnam%20was%20today%20officially%20announced%20as%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20prosperous%20city-state's%20presidential%20election%20on%20September%201%2C%20along%20with%20two%20Chinese-origin%20former%20business%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharman%2C%2066%2C%20former%20investment%20chief%20of%20state-owned%20company%20Ng%20Kok%20Song%2C%2075%2C%20and%20former%20head%20of%20the%20state-run%20insurance%20company%20Tan%20Kin%20Lian%2C%2075%2C%20were%20officially%20announced%20as%20candidates%20by%20the%20Elections%20Department%20(ELD)%20for%20Singapore's%20highest%20but%20non-political%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20three%20have%20been%20officially%20announced%20as%20candidates%2C%20they%20cannot%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20race%20without%20forfeiting%20their%20election%20deposits%20of%20SGD%2040%2C500%20each%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20The%20Straits%20Times%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20men%2C%20each%20vying%20to%20become%20Singapore's%20ninth%20president%2C%20can%20officially%20begin%20campaigning%2C%20which%20will%20end%20on%20August%2030.%20The%20cooling-off%20day%20is%20on%20August%2031%2C%20and%20the%20Polling%20Day%20is%20on%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingapore's%20incumbent%20President%20Halimah%20Yacob's%20six-year%20term%20will%20end%20on%20September%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20after%20the%20nomination%2C%20Mr%20Tharman%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20minister%20in%20the%20ruling%20People's%20Action%20Party%20Government%2C%20said%20he%20looked%20forward%20to%20a%20dignified%20and%20honourable%20contest%2C%20focused%20on%20what%20each%20candidate%20brings%20to%20Singaporeans%20and%20what%20each%20of%20them%20brings%20to%20the%20country's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20campaign%2C%20which%20is%20dignified%20and%20honourable%2C%20and%20a%20campaign%20which%20itself%20seeks%20to%20unite%20Singaporeans%20and%20not%20divide%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharman%20later%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he%20was%20running%20for%20the%20presidency%20not%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20new%20positions%20or%20statements%20but%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20long-held%20purpose%20in%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20in%20a%20fairer%2C%20more%20compassionate%20and%20more%20inclusive%20society.%20And%20my%20life%20is%20dedicated%20to%20that.%20Singapore%20can%20be%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20Mr%20Tharman%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharman%2C%20who%20resigned%20from%20all%20political%20and%20public%20offices%20in%20July%20to%20contest%20for%20the%20presidency%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20future%20that%20we%20are%20concerned%20about%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20different%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20a%20more%20difficult%20and%20challenging%20future%20that%20we%20face%2C%20which%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20I%20have%20entered%20this%20contest%20to%20offer%20all%20my%20experience%20and%20capabilities%20on%20the%20ground%20for%20a%20few%20decades%20nationally%20and%20internationally%2C%26quot%3B%20Channel%20News%20Asia%20quoted%20Mr%20Tharman%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20I%20can%20serve%20Singaporeans%20in%20the%20role%20of%20President%20with%20all%20my%20heart%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharman%20was%20an%20economist%20and%20civil%20servant%2C%20mainly%20at%20the%20Monetary%20Authority%20of%20Singapore%2C%20before%20joining%20politics%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20served%20as%20Minister%20for%20Education%20and%20Finance%20and%20was%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20from%202011%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENg%2C%20who%20introduced%20himself%20in%20Chinese%2C%20Malay%20and%20Tamil%2C%20said%20he%20was%20standing%20for%20president%20to%20protect%20Singapore's%20three%20national%20treasures%20-the%20reserves%2C%20public%20service%20appointments%20and%20social%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20I'm%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20really%20serve%20the%20people%20of%20Singapore.%20So%2C%20I%20feel%20excited%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Singapore%20are%20giving%20me%20this%20opportunity%20to%20serve%20my%20country%20one%20more%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETan%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20the%20people%20of%20Singapore%20%26quot%3Ba%20chance%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20president%20who%20is%20truly%20independent%20of%20the%20ruling%20government%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20if%20elected%2C%20will%20carry%20out%20his%20duties%2C%20as%20set%20out%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20diligently%2C%20honestly%2C%20and%20to%20the%20best%20of%20his%20ability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20duties%20are%20to%20safeguard%20the%20reserves%20and%20uphold%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20public%20service.%20I%20ask%20for%20your%20support%20so%20that%20I%20can%20do%20my%20best%20for%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20non-political%20office%2C%20the%20President%20is%20responsible%20for%20several%20critical%20functions%20in%20the%20city-state%2C%20including%20key%20state%20appointments%20and%20guarding%20the%20national%20reserves%20that%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20can%20only%20use%20with%20presidential%20consensus.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fs5ujn64_-tharman-shanmugaratnam_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-origin-ex-minister-tharman-shanmugaratnam-in-final-3-way-race-to-be-singapore-president-4318507%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singapore-born%20Indian-origin%20Tharman%20Shanmugaratnam%20was%20today%20officially%20announced%20as%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20prosperous%20city-state's%20presidential%20election%20on%20September%201%2C%20along%20with%20two%20Chinese-orig