%20of%20a%20few%20days%20assumes%20significance%20given%20the%20expectation%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20meet%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20three-day%20BRICS%20summit%2C%20which%20began%20in%20Johannesburg%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitary%20officials%20from%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20entrusted%20with%20the%20responsibility%20to%20find%20a%20workable%20solution%20that%20could%20be%20implemented%20along%20the%20undemarcated%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fdepsang-on-table-india-china-hold-third-meet-in-4-days-537029%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20April%202020%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20border%20standoff%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh.%20There%20are%20particular%20differences%20over%20pulling%20troops%20back%20from%20the%20Depsang%20plains%20and%20Charding%20Nullah%20near%20Demchok.%20The%20dispute%20is%20concerning%20a%20972%20sq%20km%20plateau%20Depsang.%20Both%20have%20issues%20regarding%20troop%20positions%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20eastern%20edge%20of%20Depsang.%20India%20has%20been%20opposed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Army%20deliberating%20preventing%20the%20movement%20of%20Indian%20patrols%20on%20the%20patrolling%20route%20that%20goes%20east%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D%20in%20Depsang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20April%202020%2C%20when%20the%20standoff%20began%2C%20Indian%20patrols%20had%20been%20using%20the%20patrolling%20route.%20However%2C%20since%20then%2C%20China%20has%20been%20referring%20to%20a%20controversial%2030-year-old%20border%20agreement%20to%20prevent%20the%20movement%20of%20Indian%20patrols.%20According%20to%20the%20said%20agreement%2C%20patrolling%20parties%20of%20one%20side%20should%20return%20upon%20encountering%20the%20patrol%20party%20of%20the%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20crucial%20things%20that%20came%20up%20during%20the%20discussion%20was%20that%20the%20Indian%20troops%20would%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Chinese%20when%20patrols%20go%20east%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D.%20This%20means%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20buffer%20zone%2C%20and%20patrols%20cannot%20be%20held%20independently%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20have%20competing%20claims%20in%20the%20region%2C%20particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20Depsang%20plains.%20Some%20of%20these%20contested%20points%20have%20great%20strategic%20value%2C%20for%20they%20overlook%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20plateau%20which%20is%20under%20the%20illegal%20control%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20sources%2C%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdefence-india-china-eastern-ladakh-disengagement-talks-promoting-confidence-and-cooperation-for-border-stability-3215648%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Major%20General%20Prasanna%20Mishra%20represented%20the%20Indian%20delegation%20for%20%E2%80%9Cengaging%20in%20productive%20deliberations%20with%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%E2%80%9D.%20Major%20General%20Mishra%20commands%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%203%20Division%2C%20which%20is%20tasked%20with%20securing%20and%20managing%20the%20832-kilometer-long%20LAC%20specifically%20within%20the%20Ladakh%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20proposing%20to%20China%20that%20a%20phased%20three-step%20process%20is%20necessary%20to%20resolve%20the%20standoff.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20includes%20the%20disengagement%20of%20troops%20within%20close%20proximity%20in%20grey%20zones%20along%20the%20LAC%20and%20moving%20back%20to%20positions%20as%20on%20April%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20two%20steps%2C%20India%20suggests%20that%20there%20should%20be%20de-escalation%20and%20de-induction%2C%20which%20includes%20pul