ice%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindu%20organisations%20leaders%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20actor%20in%20Banahatti%20police%20station%20of%20Bagalkote%20district%20and%20have%20demanded%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20actor%20on%20Sunday%20took%20to%20microblogging%20site%20X%2C%20sharing%20a%20caricature%20of%20a%20man%20in%20a%20shirt%20and%20lungi%20pouring%20tea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20picture%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20view%20just%20arrived%20from%20Chandrayaan%20..%20%23VikramLander%20%23justasking.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5CnPrakash%20Raj%20has%20been%20facing%20heavy%20backlash%20since%20then%20with%20people%20saying%20that%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20country's%20pride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaced%20with%20social%20media%20outrage%20Prakash%20Raj%20clarified%20on%20X%20that%20his%20comments%20were%20only%20intended%20as%20a%20joke.%20%26quot%3BHate%20sees%20only%20Hate...I%20was%20referring%20to%20a%20joke%20of%20%23Armstrong%20times%20celebrating%20our%20kerala%20Chaiwala-which%20Chaiwala%20did%20the%20Trolls%20see%3F%20if%20you%20dont%20get%20a%20joke%20then%20the%20joke%20is%20on%20you..GROW%20UP%20%23justasking%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20set%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon%20on%20August%2023%2C%20around%2018%3A04%20hours%20IST.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELive%20action%20will%20be%20available%20on%20the%20ISRO%20website%2C%20its%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20public%20broadcaster%20DD%20National%20TV%20from%2017%3A27%20IST%20on%20Aug%2023%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20be%20the%20fourth%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat%20after%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20China%2C%20but%20India%20will%20be%20the%20only%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20south%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20objectives%20of%C2%A0Chandrayaan-3%C2%A0mission%20are%20threefold%20--%20to%20demonstrate%20safe%20and%20soft%20landing%20on%20lunar%20surface%3B%20to%20demonstrate%C2%A0rover%C2%A0roving%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20and%20to%20conduct%20in-situ%20scientific%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3's%20development%20phase%20commenced%20in%20January%202020%20with%20the%20launch%20planned%20sometime%20in%202021.%20However%2C%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20brought%20an%20unforeseen%20delay%20to%20the%20mission's%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%C2%A0mission%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%2C%202023%20via%20the%20GSLV%20Mark%203%20(LVM%203)%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota%20at%202%3A35%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692692760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Fim842bf8_prakash-raj_625x300_21_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-filed-against-actor-prakash-raj-for-mocking-chandrayaan-3-4318361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Prakash%20Raj%20has%20been%20booked%20in%20a%20police%20station%20of%20Karnataka's%20Bagalkot%20district%20over%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20in%20which%20he%20allegedly%20mocked%20India's%20ambitious%20third%20lunar%20mission--%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A162%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-filed-against-actor-prakash-raj-for-mocking-chandrayaan-3-4318361%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-filed-against-actor-prakash-raj-f