airs%20has%20appointed%20an%20Assam%20Police%20officer%20on%20deputation%20at%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20after%20she%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guwahatiplus.com%2Fcontroversy-surrounds-nia-deputation-of-assam-police-officer-implicated-in-apsc-scam%5C%22%3Enamed%20by%20a%20judicial%20commission%20in%20a%20high-profile%20corruption%20case.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20officer%2C%20Rumi%20Timungpi%2C%20was%20grilled%20by%20the%20one-man%20judicial%20commission%20led%20by%20retired%20judge%20Justice%20Biplab%20Sarma%20for%20about%20four%20hours%20in%20July%202021.%20Her%20interrogation%20was%20based%20on%20her%20written%20reply%20sought%20by%20the%20commission.%20She%20was%20then%20serving%20as%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%20at%20the%20special%20branch%20of%20Assam%20Police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell-known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98APSC%20scam%E2%80%99%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20multi-crore%20corruption%20case%20was%20the%20first%20big%20stab%20at%20the%20former%20Congress%20regime%20by%20the%20first%20BJP-led%20government%20by%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%20in%202016.%20The%20state%20police%2C%20led%20by%20Sonowal%20as%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20had%20arrested%20not%20just%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Commission%2C%20Rakesh%20Paul%2C%20but%20also%2021%20officers%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20state%20administration%20through%20the%20APSC%20route%20in%202013.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20charge%20against%20those%20serving%20officers%20was%20that%20they%20had%20bribed%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Commission%20even%20after%20failing%20to%20clear%20the%20qualifying%20examination.%20Timungpi%20was%20one%20of%20the%2021%20officers%20named%20by%20the%20Commission%20appointed%20by%20the%20Sonowal%20government.%20The%20ruling%20BJP%20had%20gone%20hammer%20and%20tongs%20at%20the%20Tarun%20Gogoi-led%20regime%20for%20indulging%20in%20corruption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pratidintime.com%2Fnational%2Fcontroversial-cop-rumir-timungpi-apsc-scam-appointed-nia-asp%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPratidin%20Time%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20report%20by%20Justice%20Sarma%20Commission%20brought%20to%20light%20the%20explosive%20fact%20that%20Timungpi%20failed%20to%20even%20clear%20the%20APSC%20examination%E2%80%9D.%20She%20has%20since%20contested%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20the%20case%20is%20going%20on%20at%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20the%20MHA%20appointed%20her%20on%20June%2015%20as%20additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20at%20the%20NIA%20%E2%80%9Con%20deputation%20basis%20for%20three%20years.%E2%80%9D%20The%20appointment%20has%20come%20through%20after%20a%20clearance%20given%20by%20the%20state%20home%20department.%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20is%20also%20the%20state%20home%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20Assam%20government%20notification%20this%20August%2011%20stated%20that%20she%20had%20been%20released%20from%20duty%20by%20Assam%20Police%20to%20take%20up%20the%20new%20assignment%20at%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20on%20how%20a%20controversial%20cop%20has%20been%20assigned%20an%20important%20position%20in%20a%20central%20agency%20like%20NIA%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassamtribune.com%2Fassam%2Fcop-accused-in-apsc-cash-for-job-scam-appointed-as-nia-asp-1490756%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAssam%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0This%20March%2C%20then%20APSC%20chairman%20Paul%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pratidintime.com%2Fguwahati-news-breaking-latest%2Frakesh-paul-released-after-6-years-in-jail-for-apsc-scam%5C%22%3Ereleased%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20bail%20after%20over%20s