%20by%20God.%20He%20is%20doing%20commendable%20work%20for%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs.%20Shaikh%20had%20earlier%20said%20her%20first%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20with%20PM%20Modi%20was%20when%20he%20was%20an%20RSS%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaksha%20Bandhan%20marks%20the%20bond%20of%20love%20between%20siblings%20and%20will%20be%20celebrated%20on%20August%2030%20this%20year.%20Sisters%20tie%20a%20%3Cem%3Erakhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20their%20brothers'%20wrists%20and%20pray%20for%20their%20prosperity%20and%20longevity.%20In%20return%2C%20the%20brothers%20pledge%20to%20protect%20and%20support%20the%20sisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692690780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fnm0ssfi_qamar-mohsin-sheikh_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-raksha-bandhan-pm-modis-pakistani-sister-to-visit-delhi-to-tie-him-rakhi-4318354%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Qamar%20Mohsin%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20Pakistan-origin%20woman%20who%20moved%20to%20Ahmedabad%20after%20her%20marriage%2Chas%20been%20tying%20a%20rakhi%20to%20PM%20Modi%20for%20over%2030%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-raksha-bandhan-pm-modis-pakistani-sister-to-visit-delhi-to-tie-him-rakhi-4318354%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-raksha-bandhan-pm-modis-pakistani-sister-to-visit-delhi-to-tie-him-rakhi-4318354%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-raksha-bandhan-pm-modis-pakistani-sister-to-visit-delhi-to-tie-him-rakhi-4318354%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIC%20acquires%206.66%25%20stake%20in%20Jio%20Financial%20Services%20through%20demerger%20process%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692690562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2