me%20over%20the%20NSCN-IM%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20compromise%20on%20its%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20constitution%20and%20recognition%20of%20the%20NSCN-IM%E2%80%99s%20flag%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-nscn-im-look-to-revive-naga-peace-talks-101692642922510.html%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20quoting%20NSCN-IM%20sources%2C%20said%20the%20meetings%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20to%20be%20suspended%20as%20Mishra%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20advisor%20(northeast)%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20had%20to%20direct%20his%20attention%20to%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%5BT%5Dhe%20two%20sides%20had%20made%20significant%20progress%2C%20particularly%20on%20NSCN-IM%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20Naga%20flag%20and%20constitution.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2014%20this%20year%2C%20the%20day%20the%20NSCN-IM%20celebrates%20as%20its%20Independence%20Day%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukhrultimes.com%2Ffull-speech-of-nscn-im-supremo-th-muivah-77th-naga-independence-day-celebration%2F%5C%22%3E%20Muivah%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20flag%20and%20constitution%20are%20naturally%20inseparable%20from%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20a%20people.%20It%20is%20universally%20an%20accepted%20truth%20that%20flag%20and%20constitution%20are%20constituent%20parts%20of%20sovereignty.%20There%20is%20no%20ambiguity%20about%20it.%20The%20Indian%20leaders%20understand%20it%20too.%20They%20must%20take%20the%20stand%20to%20speak%20the%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20Naga%20talks%20are%20being%20formally%20resumed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20neighbours%20in%20the%20Manipur%20hills%2C%20the%20Kukis%2C%20have%20begun%20demanding%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20administration%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20peace%20talks%20with%20armed%20Kuki%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20led%20by%20Mishra%20for%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20on%20August%2017%20%E2%80%93%20a%20proposed%20map%20for%20a%20a%20Kuki%20state%20was%20submitted.%20As%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20was%20a%20significant%20move%20by%20Kuki%20political%20leaders.%20However%2C%20the%20map%20includes%20certain%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20which%20the%20Nagas%20consider%20as%20their%20own%20traditional%20land.%20These%20claims%20over%20land%20are%20increasingly%20leading%20to%20growing%20division%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20in%20the%20strife-torn%20state%2C%20with%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%20(UNC)%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20the%20Nagas%20in%20Manipur%2C%20issuing%20a%20fresh%20statement%20on%20the%20matter%20this%20August%2021%2C%20criticising%20Kukis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWarning%20the%20Kukis%20that%20%E2%80%9CNagas%20will%20not%20remain%20mute%20over%20the%20issue%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20UNC%20statement%20said%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20lies%2C%20lop-sided%20history%20and%20fabricated%20information%20contained%20in%20every%20statement%20and%20memorandum%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20tantamount%20to%20distortion%20of%20Naga%20history%20and%20insult%20to%20the%20Naga%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20open%20opposition%20to%20the%20Kuki%20move%20by%20UNC%20is%20noteworthy%20as%20the%20body%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20extremely%20close%20to%20the%20NSCN-IM.%20These%20areas%20in%20Manipur%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20NSCN-IM%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cgreater%20Nagalim%E2%80%9D%20demand.%20Muivah%E2%80%99s%20August%2014%20speech%20had%20underlined%20that%20demand%20when%20he%20said%2C%20