ver%20land%20are%20increasingly%20leading%20to%20growing%20division%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20in%20the%20strife-torn%20state%2C%20with%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%20(UNC)%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20the%20Nagas%20in%20Manipur%2C%20issuing%20a%20fresh%20statement%20on%20the%20matter%20this%20August%2021%2C%20criticising%20Kukis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWarning%20the%20Kukis%20that%20%E2%80%9CNagas%20will%20not%20remain%20mute%20over%20the%20issue%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20UNC%20statement%20said%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20lies%2C%20lop-sided%20history%20and%20fabricated%20information%20contained%20in%20every%20statement%20and%20memorandum%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20tantamount%20to%20distortion%20of%20Naga%20history%20and%20insult%20to%20the%20Naga%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20open%20opposition%20to%20the%20Kuki%20move%20by%20UNC%20is%20noteworthy%20as%20the%20body%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20extremely%20close%20to%20the%20NSCN-IM.%20These%20areas%20in%20Manipur%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20NSCN-IM%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cgreater%20Nagalim%E2%80%9D%20demand.%20Muivah%E2%80%99s%20August%2014%20speech%20had%20underlined%20that%20demand%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20issue%20of%20integration%20of%20all%20Naga%20areas%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20officially%20acknowledged%20that%20it%20is%20the%20legitimate%20right%20of%20the%20Nagas%20and%20therefore%2C%20it%20shall%20be%20finalised%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Naga%20talks%20are%20being%20held%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20Framework%20Agreement%20signed%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20with%20NSCN-IM%20in%20August%202015.%20Since%20then%2C%20though%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20talks%20have%20taken%20place%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20both%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20in%20Nagaland%20and%20with%20a%20number%20of%20Union%20government-appointed%20interlocutors%20and%20also%20with%20some%20other%20Naga%20armed%20groups%2C%20not%20much%20headway%20has%20been%20made%20so%20far.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692687080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fmodi_muivah_20150817_350_630.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-violence-naga-kuki-peace-talks-muivah-nscn-im%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kukis'%20claims%20over%20some%20stretches%20of%20land%20in%20Manipur%20is%20leading%20to%20division%20in%20the%20strife-torn%20state.%20The%20United%20Naga%20Council%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20the%20Nagas%20in%20Manipur%2C%20issued%20a%20fresh%20statement%20on%20the%20matter%20on%20August%2021%2C%20criticising%20Kukis.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-violence-naga-kuki-peace-talks-muivah-nscn-im%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tollywood%20celebrities%20shower%20love%20on%20Chiranjeevi's%2068th%20birthday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692686499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102933258%2Cimgsize-34748.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fallu-arjun-jr-ntr-pawan-kalyan-and-other-tollywood-celebrities-shower-love-on-chiranjeevis-68th-birthday%2Farticleshow%2F102932724.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Megastar%20Chiranjeevi%20celebrated%20his%2068th%20birthday%2C%20with%20his%20real%20name%20being%20Konidela%20Sivasankara%20Varaprasad.%20He%20embarked%20on%20his%20acting%20journey%20in%201978%20with%20'Punadhirallu%2C'%20although%20'Pranam%20Khareedu'%20preceded%20it%20at%20the%20box%20office.%20He%20recently%20appeared%20in%20%26quot%3BBholaa%20Shankar%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20an%20impressive%20filmography%20o