725%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Officially%20Announces%20it%20Has%20Scrapped%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18164526%2FFwBN2HcakAEGvBw.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Karnataka%20government%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2021%2C%20has%20officially%20announced%20that%20it%20has%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%20and%20come%20out%20with%20a%20state%20education%20policy%20that%20would%20be%20in%20place%20for%20implementation%20from%20the%20next%20academic%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fexpert-committee-on-state-education-policy-in-a-week-2655640%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20the%20Union%20government%20cannot%20frame%20policies%20on%20education%2C%20which%20is%20a%20state%20subject.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20NEP%20was%20framed%20without%20taking%20states%20into%20confidence.%20An%20education%20policy%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20imposed%20on%20states.%20A%20uniform%20policy%20is%20not%20possible%20in%20a%20diverse%2C%20plural%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20not%20failing%20to%20add%20that%20that%20states%20like%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20already%20rejected%20the%20NEP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigher%20education%20minister%20M.C.%20Sudhakar%20said%20no%20names%20were%20proposed%20or%20discussed%20in%20the%20meeting%20for%20the%20expert%20committee.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20consider%20all%20stakeholders%20while%20framing%20the%20policy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20According%20to%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20refer%20to%20an%20October%202016%20report%20on%20Karnataka%20State%20Education%20Policy%20prepared%20by%20the%20former%