up%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20training%20people%20on%20setting%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F265639%2Fsandeep-kannan-vyavasai-bhoomi-tirupati-hydroponics-startup-farmer-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20fodder%20%3C%2Fa%3Esystems%2C%20Ashwin%20also%20offers%20consultation%20and%20installation%20services%20across%20India%20and%20in%20countries%20like%20Oman%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20clock%20Rs%202%20crore%20in%20revenue%20last%20year.%20This%20year%2C%20he%20projects%20an%20income%20boost%20to%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20came%20back%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20my%20family%20was%20shocked%20at%20my%20decision%20to%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20where%20my%20salary%20package%20was%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20per%20annum.%20For%20eight%20years%20between%202011%20and%202019%2C%20I%20hardly%20earned%20any%20income%20from%20my%20hydroponics%20venture.%20Moreover%2C%20I%20invested%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20%E2%80%94%20some%20from%20my%20savings%20and%20the%20rest%20loaned%20from%20my%20family%20members.%20It%20is%20only%20in%20the%20past%20four%20years%20that%20I%20started%20earning%20a%20profit%20from%20this%20work.%20But%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20work%20that%20I%20put%20in%20throughout%20these%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20extremely%20satisfying%20to%20see%20that%20today%2C%20people%20in%20India%20are%20as%20fascinated%20by%20hydroponics%20as%20I%20was%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwin%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Ashwin%20Sawant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692337771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fashwin-sawant-3-1692278469.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.c