ys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20study%20and%20found%20that%2094%20percent%20of%20parents%20from%20various%20cities%20we%20are%20working%20in%20saw%20improvement%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20of%20the%20students.%20Our%20training%20methods%20make%20young%20people%20confident.%20These%20experiences%20give%20us%20hope.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20about%20the%20happiness%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20our%20students%20and%20the%20freshness%20we%20are%20able%20to%20bring%20into%20classrooms.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20someone%20who%20wants%20a%20strong%20purpose%20to%20live%2C%20and%20when%20you%20find%20the%20impact%2C%20you%20are%20motivated%20to%20do%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rennis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Rennis%20Joseph.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691646234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-3-1691584758.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326816%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Teaching%20English%20to%20refugees%20during%20his%20college%20days%20set%20Hyderabad-based%20Rennis%20Joseph%20down%20the%20path%20of%20starting%20Ignis%20Careers%2C%20which%20teaches%203.5%20lakh%20children%20from%20low-cost%20schools%20across%20India%20English%20language%20and%20life%20skills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A59%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326816%2Frennis-joseph-started-ignis-careers-to-help-children-learn-english-pursue-higher-education%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Southern%20Airways%20Express%20Is%20Suing%20Former%20Pilots%20For%20Training%20Costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Florida-based%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20enforce%20a%20controversial%20employment%20clause%20that%20has%20gained%20national%20attention%